SELECT processed_date, SUM(record_count) AS processed_row_count, ( SELECT COUNT(1) FROM sales.transactions WHERE DATE(created_date) = DATE(DATE_SUB(NOW(), INTERVAL 1 DAY)) AND processed_date = sales.process_log.processed_date ) AS transactions_row_count FROM sales.process_log WHERE 1=1 AND processed_date = DATE(NOW()) GROUP BY processed_date;
